{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a88e8bbcb1cb7cfad46657c9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨的梦想",
        "text_hash": "6a27baf941e6a3ad123b96b8e59d7144de17966aecbd0063bd8c7393c5d907cc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d559b22772b69088bb343428",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨的母亲怀孕了。她一只手放在肚子上，凝望着自己贫瘠的村庄。远处，一面莫桑比克国旗从旗杆上无力地垂下来。",
        "text_hash": "70c24dcfa3a628930e04dc6630424007698f60d1c8f7260908a93702d514dae7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9996220d698a796560ccf0f9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨即将出生在莫桑比克的一个小村庄里。这个国家很贫穷，人民还不能自己治理自己。孩子们没有好的学校，许多人不会读书。格拉萨的母亲梦想着给自己的孩子更好的机会。但没有教育，就几乎没有希望。",
        "text_hash": "944417b056109016f58114fb5983d4e7c690b43a425ce8aecc013421296d4ce5",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_9ba4a5947f5defe7caa98110",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨怀孕的母亲和五个兄弟姐妹站在父亲的病床旁哭泣。他们的父亲梦想着自己的孩子们能够读书。",
        "text_hash": "a8ff91f4c165754627acd9f0c297f00dc765350ee8f04d98b79323dff619d515",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d98735d34aa81ca9f6cd8b44",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "婴儿格拉萨将是第六个孩子。但在这件喜事到来的同时，也有巨大的悲伤。他们深爱的父亲快要去世了。他梦想着自己最小的女儿能去一所好学校。他知道，教育会给她带来他从未拥有过的机会。他的家人承诺，要让他们父亲的梦想成真。",
        "text_hash": "8081a97f61322db1542cc15f32ad25015678885cb5845f7fc0ad28feb672a9aa",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ae36543ea431840242b2e24e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "小格拉萨坐在母亲的身上。她的母亲正在读一个故事。",
        "text_hash": "a1b5545a146bf472ecbd99bf6a9d7c625b96c68ef522a4167595a2a5828c8f8f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_68c62bba6318dc6953334345",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "就在父亲去世几周后，这个新生儿出生了。她得到了一个与她的美丽和祝福相配的名字——格拉萨。随着岁月流逝，格拉萨给家人带来了许多欢乐，而家人也遵守了对父亲许下的承诺。格拉萨将接受良好的教育。",
        "text_hash": "038b894d603011d4d42700db89717c27aebccfda8b03bb7a65f0759180f3bc70",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f0290eb0345402f95341f478",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨坐在一间设备齐全的教室第一排，身边是白人孩子。她的老师站在他们面前。",
        "text_hash": "dd094ec87ac88e6426cb39da420a83794565e62967d7d559b06dff8be93b15c3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_263a4c8f4bf6644376f1a966",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨在学校努力学习，十几岁时，她收到了一份将改变她一生的礼物。那是一份去富裕城市学校就读的奖学金。",
        "text_hash": "7537478d1eb741515e954f5be0226b6413d0c8ac1ca2b15e713b7e6f7ab63cff",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2714d82ec21a9b8db77a4ee7",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "她梦想成为一名教师，用自己的教育去教育别人。她希望她深爱的莫桑比克的孩子们懂得阅读和学习。她梦想有一天所有孩子都能上学。",
        "text_hash": "f74e1dd12adfc2ed657b46405d4ebc1aa0650af8125ec7c564bbd233cf88914b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a73ca46f96587c93c345e35f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "戴着眼镜的格拉萨坐在图书馆的书桌旁，周围满是书。",
        "text_hash": "d7ccbcf6a8e917713d5c37bff3efa6173c904554b5a23ada1f9c267f56a73969",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e756d7d1fb068b733976daba",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨在那所城市学校里尽了最大努力，几年后，她再次受到眷顾。那是另一份奖学金，让她去遥远的葡萄牙上大学。她结识了新朋友，学习了新语言，阅读了大量书籍。她实现了成为教师的梦想。",
        "text_hash": "b61e0723e7182c5a8479e6a07fe1a4097f653a954abc2647aa599a228ade1155",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5740bf5a00c376e7bfad292a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这一切让格拉萨非常快乐。只有一件事仍然让她难过……",
        "text_hash": "7bb61bbffab45bd238ab3e10e8512bab472b2512aebd988c6eebf62b72606d88",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3f285f7739933f3c3d5b4acf",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨站在树荫下，教村里的妇女和孩子们学习。",
        "text_hash": "16e6c003d4b45a465aed16b0147f44b40bfc22db1b6f6c889a0eb2d081d268a8",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3d2946bccc60693580b5cb19",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在家乡，人们仍然没有自由。但现在，格拉萨拥有了教育、技能和希望。她也有一些朋友，他们和她一样认同儿童学习的权利。她将运用自己的知识，并与朋友们一起工作。他们将共同为莫桑比克带来改变。",
        "text_hash": "0d00dfea5c84e11c049fd1249aec4a13cf3ec6228ea12e9ac7d716d51f37be31",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a00ea9053d2f8cf718056a28",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "快乐的公民微笑着挥舞莫桑比克国旗。",
        "text_hash": "df72a3f3e227cea2846ac084a1a88d39f4fbacf6dcb85fff21e029cdbdebfdb3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6fec578372c5a424066b4095",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "终于，在她所有朋友的帮助下，莫桑比克获得了自由！",
        "text_hash": "4abac1623315661462e5be56b35788280506b25ce18041464d328cd486492108",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_17d730b262a0ed68759579f4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨和萨莫拉在婚礼当天拥抱在一起。他们梦想着将来一起居住的房子。",
        "text_hash": "48893be326a04ccecd02909596284bfd4850ed81b68b424cf9fc00b404ff7e9d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8c331387ed66306e159afd8b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "被选中领导这个国家的人，是格拉萨特别的朋友萨莫拉·马谢尔。他们相爱并结婚了。",
        "text_hash": "54b1af0c1d571485dc987c57a02ac018d42842e9ac12914d8fd462f162fbf5fe",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f555c2ba8e7237d58eca0203",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "没有书的孩子们看起来很难过。拥有书的孩子们快乐而自豪。",
        "text_hash": "47737d860d8cb596536199558fff7c15def76dc0b2d5ccb79f5a4daa048b95d9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3a1f6b029b5c8ededa9755a9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨被赋予了一项重要工作：确保莫桑比克所有孩子都能接受良好的教育。这是一项艰巨的工作，因为莫桑比克有那么多孩子不会读书。她知道他们需要教育，也想在自己的国家带来真正的改变。她从小学开始，让男孩和女孩都走进教室。识字是她关注的重点，把书放到孩子们手中也是她的重点。",
        "text_hash": "a953b3e0c62460cf89a3269dbe7e256a28ae158ad17f28532c3c8b45459cc4f2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0079fcaeb1fd23bf57ccc481",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨和萨莫拉坐在沙发上给他们的两个年幼孩子读书。远处，一架飞机在停机坪上爆炸。",
        "text_hash": "3d946782fae4aebbdc61ccb81d3cdd1cada55788c96d5a945fb30669b37e1391",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7953cd828d36c770b244a9ae",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨和萨莫拉有两个孩子。他们共同怀有一个梦想：为自己的家庭和莫桑比克人民创造美好的生活。他们快乐而充满希望。",
        "text_hash": "deb099ded3f5b547b23e8ae54ec2445d479efe7527220d7ad6997be314ca9183",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_272eab7152839e2cf3877627",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "后来，在一个可怕的日子里，萨莫拉死于一场飞机失事。",
        "text_hash": "7f05616d0b2e3b89caf24b2e2461afa236b6242e3699060e8e9506d3b9f499b7",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_12380b4b06aa179e3de2c82d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "年长一些的格拉萨和纳尔逊·曼德拉站在田野里，身边是一群快乐的孩子。",
        "text_hash": "62aa07c051480d0b07278bcb88f3f398b646e374d432410efc6b093380171d21",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f9129708ab239f406de7604b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨为萨莫拉哀悼了许多年，但她再次找到了爱。她遇到了一位男子，他也一生都梦想着为自己的人民带来自由、希望和教育。",
        "text_hash": "c4436d96450bd07953e22657e8bc5a777d8085e7461c35ff0f7df0af8cf619fd",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_382be61f89c502daf4404396",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨嫁给了纳尔逊·曼德拉，他们一起努力帮助非洲的孩子们。",
        "text_hash": "36412b509d5ab3d9161e5df665791f9ab56cb3518f069cc1c42787fcb162d712",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e95c573399c9d412b4eb4192",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "格拉萨把书分发给她村里的孩子们。到处都能看到孩子们在读书。",
        "text_hash": "7136bfab3e0388255dc4e94d11760a2d7d6aa7cefbd3f2503b16595536348d20",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_979aa45b51eb3fdaec5aa4fd",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这是一本书，我的孩子。它会激励你去做什么呢？",
        "text_hash": "d0a6b529ecb419565a6f012d95394cbe1e2a6eea42eb07ff094b8aa444a908d1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_1628221f8b4396ea02c2efd5"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    }
  ],
